  "title": "Motschen's Puddles",
  "description": "Adds puddles that spawn during rain and thunder! Compatible with any shader pack!",
  "body": "<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod adds puddles which spawn during rainy weather and makes snow layers pile up during snow storms.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The puddle is a new block that you can interact with while holding an empty bottle to fill the bottle with water.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This was inspired by <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/puddles\">Puddles</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/QHWqXv6/puddle-banner.png\" width=\"768\" height=\"132\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/535D1YoA/images/c0e0dc314c0cea3a4a0d2bfd2a6595cbc05ac60a.png\" width=\"655\" height=\"368\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/Motschen/Assets/blob/main/quilt+fabric-banner.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" height=\"56\" /></p>",
